sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller
    participant I as Inference plugin
    participant H as aroundCompletion
    participant W as Workflow
    participant L as LLM

    C->>I: chatComplete
    I->>H: invokeHook — blocks until complete
    H->>W: execute
    W-->>W: anonymize
    W->>H: call_site.proceed step
    H->>I: invoke proceedFn
    I->>L: connector call (buffered)
    Note over I,L: Stream buffered — response assembled<br/>before step output resolves
    L-->>I: full assembled response
    I-->>H: assembled response
    H-->>W: step output
    W-->>W: restore (expressions resolve)
    W-->>W: workflow.output
    W-->>H: result
    H-->>I: hook result
    I-->>C: result (no streaming — TTFT = full pipeline)
